Package: PLSsemEngine
Type: Package
Title: A Transparent PLSsemEngine for Composite-Based Mode A Estimation
Version: 1.2.0
Date: 2026-04-25
Authors@R: 
    person("Manuel", "Soto-Perez", 
           email = "msoto@up.edu.mx", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A transparent and modular implementation of Partial Least Squares 
    Structural Equation Modeling (PLS-SEM) focused on reflective measurement 
    models (Mode A)[cite: 4, 25]. The package separates estimation, bootstrap inference, 
    and predictive evaluation into independent components, emphasising 
    algorithmic transparency, reproducibility, and researcher-controlled analysis[cite: 6, 59].
